-- SPD Won’t Back Fiscal Pact Without Transaction Tax, Spiegel Says
-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 2012-05-25T06:00:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-25/spd-won-t-back-fiscal-pact-without-transaction-tax-spiegel-says.html
The German opposition Social
Democrats won’t vote to ratify  Europe ’s fiscal compact without
the addition of a financial transaction tax and growth-friendly
measures,  Der Spiegel  reported, citing an interview with leader
Frank-Walter Steinmeier.  To contact the reporter on this story:
